item.title: Python & Neovim
item.description: Python & Neovim What do you need to have? Hej, today we begin learning with Nutek to be able to use it how I see it fit. First be sure you have one of the following: neosb/nutek-core:0.4.0 from Docker Hub Nutek from crates.io or Github You could follow on with Python3, pip, venv and Neovim What you will learn? I want to show you few Python use cases and how to write code in Neovim.
